    "JCal is a fork of the original open-source project by Avraham Drissman and Frank Yellin (BSD 3-Clause License, 2018). App icon by Jomy Muttathil. Hebrew-calendar algorithms adapted from the GNU Emacs calendar code." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "machine_translated",
            "value" : "JCal est un fork du projet open-source original d’Avraham Drissman et Frank Yellin (licence BSD 3-Clause, 2018). Icône par Jomy Muttathil. Algorithmes du calendrier hébraïque adaptés du code GNU Emacs calendar."
