    },
    "Lag BaOmer (18 Iyar): the 33rd day of the Omer and a joyful pause in its semi-mourning, associated with Rabbi Shimon bar Yochai. Customs include bonfires, weddings, and outings." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "machine_translated",
            "value" : "Lag BaOmer (18 Iyar) : le 33e jour du Omer et une pause joyeuse dans son demi-deuil, associé à Rabbi Chimon bar Yohaï. Les coutumes comprennent les feux de joie, les mariages et les sorties."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Lag BaOmer: the 33rd day of the Omer, a festive break in the period of mourning." : {
